	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=3111&amp;mid=104009572957490">Easy, but not cheap</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=3111&amp;mid=104009572957490#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Mon, Dec 16th 10:53 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=194306"><span id="Scholar">DrmHntrREM</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">51 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Not *so* easy and not under 10pp either, though in THEORY it should be.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/><br/>I have nearly a level 60 skill in tailoring now, and this is trivial to me, but it had a high failure rate on it.  <br/><br/>It took me 8 spells (at 4p7s a pop, not to mention I personally had to pay more than the cost of the spell because I had to send a necro to get the spells for me in the first place) and 9 pelts (who knows how many of those wolves I had to kill to get them.  And buying would have cost at least 1p each IF you can find them at a merchant), and 8 silk swatches, which while easy to make cost no less than 1p each in the Bazaar, and hours of killing spiders to get enough silks to make them. Out of that I got one Large Shadow Silk (only tried it once, and it worked the first time) and two Shadow Silks.  <br/><br/>So that comes out to around 60pp to make 1 large shadow silk, and 2 shadow silks.  And a lot of time invested in gathering the components.  <br/><br/>I have enough now that when I get high enough to do the epic monk quest I won't be fretting over this, but I would suggest, if you don't want to waste time killing wolves and spiders and someone is offering them up at a price you can afford, take it.  <br/><br/>And speaking of shadow wolves, if I don't find a paw soon I am going to scream.  <br/><br/>Good journeys!<br/>Kaishii<br/>Human Monk</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
